   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS00048772X_0016"/>Hn Gustav Schwarzkopf</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207301">Tiefer Graben 17</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0015"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb631"><hi rend="pre-print">Freiburg i. Br.</hi></rs></p><p rend="center"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb353172"><hi rend="pre-print">Rathaus</hi></rs></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0016"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb631">Freiburg</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>13. 1. 925</date></dateline></opener><p>Nun hab ich drei <rs type="event" ref="#pmb183497 #pmb183503 #pmb183512" subtype="implied">Vorlesungen</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04356-1"/><rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb183497"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb872">Stuttgart</rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04356-1"><ref type="schnitzler-kultur" subtype="Cf" target="pmb183497"/>.</note>, <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04356-2"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb183503" subtype="implied"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb228">B.-B.</rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04356-2"><ref type="schnitzler-kultur" subtype="Cf" target="pmb183503"/>.</note> u <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04356-3"/><rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb183512"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb631">Freiburg</rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04356-3"><ref type="schnitzler-kultur" subtype="Cf" target="pmb183512"/>.</note> sehr gut hinter mir – <date>heute</date>  Abend
                  begi<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich, mit <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04356-4"/><rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb183521"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb854">Basel</rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04356-4"><ref type="schnitzler-kultur" subtype="Cf" target="pmb183521"/>.</note>, die <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs> zu beglücken.
               Befinden vortrefflich. Lassen Sie mich vielleicht nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb484">Zürich</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb236955">Hotel Gotthard</rs> mit einer
                  Zeil<unclear>e</unclear> wissen, wies bei Ihnen geht.</p><closer>Alles<lb/>herzliche. <supplied>Ihr Arthur</supplied></closer></div>
      </body>
